<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Explore the FAQ section for answers to common questions about Kiran Pratibha Scholarship 2024. Get detailed information on eligibility, application process, and more."
    />
    <meta
      name="keywords"
      content="FAQ, Kiran Pratibha Scholarship, frequently asked questions, eligibility, application process"
    />
    <title>FAQ Section</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/Pratibha/faq.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="faq-container-c1">
      <div class="faq-container-c2">
        <h1 class="faq-title">Any questions? Check out the FAQ</h1>
        <p class="faq-content">
          Certainly! The FAQ section provides answers to common questions. It
          covers a variety of topics and aims to address user queries
          efficiently.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-container-c3">
        <div class="faq-accordion">
          <div class="faq-accordion-item">
            <div class="faq-accordion-question">
              Q. Is Kiran Pratibha Scholarship awarded only to economically
              challenged students?
            </div>
            <div class="faq-accordion-answer">
              Yes, more than one student from the same family can also apply for
              the scholarship.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-accordion-item">
            <div class="faq-accordion-question">
              Q. Can more than one student from the same family apply for KPS?
            </div>
            <div class="faq-accordion-answer">
              Yes, more than one student from the same family can also apply for
              the scholarship.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-accordion-item">
            <div class="faq-accordion-question">
              Q. How long do you provide scholarship to the students?
            </div>
            <div class="faq-accordion-answer">
              Yes, more than one student from the same family can also apply for
              the scholarship.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-accordion-item">
            <div class="faq-accordion-question">
              Q. What are the major check points for scholarship?
            </div>
            <div class="faq-accordion-answer">
              Yes, more than one student from the same family can also apply for
              the scholarship.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-accordion-item">
            <div class="faq-accordion-question">
              Q. What is the expectation of Kiran Foundation from the students
              selected in KP?
            </div>
            <div class="faq-accordion-answer">
              Yes, more than one student from the same family can also apply for
              the scholarship.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script>
      document.querySelectorAll(".faq-accordion-question").forEach((item) => {
        item.addEventListener("click", (event) => {
          const accordionItem = item.parentNode;
          accordionItem.classList.toggle("active");
        });
      });
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
